        ships in 5b. Copy adapted to <b>5/Tag</b> to match the actual
        <code class="font-dmmono text-[12px]">dailyLimit: 5</code> enforced by <code class="font-dmmono text-[12px]">/api/topics/create</code> (the JSX shows
        5/Stunde, which the API never actually enforces).
      </p>
      <RateLimitPanel unlocksIn="04:47:12" client:load />
    </section>

    {/* ── 17 · Feed status footer ──────────────────────────────────── */}
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-dmmono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-mute mb-2">
        17 · Feed status footer
      </h2>
      <p class="font-bricolage text-sm text-ink-soft mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Always rendered at the bottom of the forum index. The middle slot
        carries the status indicator that switches per <code class="font-dmmono text-[12px]">mode</code>.
        <code class="font-dmmono text-[12px]">'live'</code> mode (post-just-landed celebration) is deferred to 5b
        with the optimistic compose mutation.
      </p>
      <p class="font-dmmono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink-mute mb-2">
        ◇ fresh
      </p>
      <FeedStatusFooter mode="fresh" pageCount={18} currentPage={1} minutesSinceLast={28} client:load />
      <p class="font-dmmono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink-mute mt-4 mb-2">
        ◇ loading
      </p>
      <FeedStatusFooter mode="loading" pageCount={18} currentPage={1} client:load />
      <p class="font-dmmono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink-mute mt-4 mb-2">
        ◇ offline
      </p>
      <FeedStatusFooter mode="offline" pageCount={18} currentPage={1} client:load />
      <p class="font-dmmono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink-mute mt-4 mb-2">
        ◇ live (post just landed — fires for 6 s after a successful submit)
      </p>
      <FeedStatusFooter mode="live" pageCount={18} currentPage={1} client:load />
    </section>

    {/* ── 18 · ComposeForm ─────────────────────────────────────────── */}
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-dmmono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-mute mb-2">
        18 · ComposeForm
