      <p class="font-bricolage text-sm text-ink-soft mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        The right-column preview that updates as the user types. Shown
        with a hand-typed values object so the section is static-but-
        realistic. CTA handlers are no-ops.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 border-2 border-ink rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-paper p-6 font-dmmono text-[10px] text-ink-mute">
          ◇ form column would render here at md+
        </div>
        <ComposePreview
          values={{
            title: 'Sperrmüll-Tausch Sonntag — wer macht mit?',
            body: 'Letztes Mal hab ich einen Stuhl und zwei Pflanzen mitgenommen. Wir machen das wieder am Sonntag — nehmen statt kaufen.',
            kind: 'discussion',
            tags: ['tausch', 'sonntag']
          }}
          currentUser={{ name: 'Ercan A.', image: null }}
          submitting={false}
          onPublish={() => {}}
          onSaveDraft={() => {}}
          onDiscard={() => {}}
          client:load
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ── 20 · ModeratingModal ─────────────────────────────────────── */}
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-dmmono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-mute mb-2">
        20 · ModeratingModal — 5-stage cosmetic pipeline
      </h2>
      <p class="font-bricolage text-sm text-ink-soft mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Full-viewport overlay shown for ~14–20 s during topic submission.
        Stages cascade in on a fixed schedule (~2.8 s each); the whole
        cycle parks at "all done" until the create mutation resolves.
        Sandbox preview embeds the modal inline so the design is
        auditable without a real submit.
      </p>
      <div class="relative h-[600px] border-2 border-ink rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-paper-warm">
        <ModeratingModal open={true} embedded onDismiss={() => {}} client:load />
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ── 21 · DeleteConfirmCard ───────────────────────────────────── */}
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-dmmono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-mute mb-2">
        21 · DeleteConfirmCard — type-to-confirm friction
      </h2>
      <p class="font-bricolage text-sm text-ink-soft mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Confirm button stays disabled until the user types the locale
        target word ("LÖSCHEN" / "DELETE"). Lives in the post detail
        right rail when delete-confirm is active. Matches the JSX
        sidebar exactly.
      </p>
      <div class="max-w-md border-l border-dashed border-rule">
        <DeleteConfirmCard
          replyCount={47}
          deleting={false}
          onConfirm={() => {}}
          onCancel={() => {}}
          client:load
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ── 22 · EditModeBanner ──────────────────────────────────────── */}
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-dmmono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-mute mb-2">
        22 · EditModeBanner — top bar in inline edit mode
      </h2>
      <p class="font-bricolage text-sm text-ink-soft mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Ochre top bar that appears above the post title when the author
        enters edit mode. ESC keyboard handler lives on the page, not
        the banner — the right-side label is decorative copy only.
      </p>
      <EditModeBanner client:load />
    </section>
  </main>
</KioskLayout>
